<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy - Uplo" %>
<% content_for :description, "Uplo's Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when using our AI-powered fitness social media tools." %>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
  <%= render 'shared/navigation' %>
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
      
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Account Information</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Email address and name</li>
          <li>• Professional information (fitness focus, bio, target audience)</li>
          <li>• Payment information (processed securely by Stripe)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Content You Upload</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Photos you upload for AI processing</li>
          <li>• Photo metadata (title, description, EXIF data)</li>
          <li>• Generated captions and your preferences</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Usage Information</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• How you use our service (features used, photos processed)</li>
          <li>• Technical information (browser, IP address, device type)</li>
          <li>• Usage analytics to improve our service</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong>Provide our service:</strong> Process your photos and generate personalized captions</li>
          <li>• <strong>Improve AI quality:</strong> Train our models to better understand fitness content</li>
          <li>• <strong>Customer support:</strong> Help you with questions and technical issues</li>
          <li>• <strong>Account management:</strong> Process payments and manage subscriptions</li>
          <li>• <strong>Product updates:</strong> Notify you of new features and improvements</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We do not sell your personal information. We may share information in these limited circumstances:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong>Service providers:</strong> OpenAI for AI processing, Stripe for payments</li>
          <li>• <strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
          <li>• <strong>Business transfers:</strong> In case of merger or acquisition</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information, including encryption in transit and at rest. 
          However, no internet transmission is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong>Account data:</strong> Retained while your account is active</li>
          <li>• <strong>Photos:</strong> Deleted 30 days after account closure</li>
          <li>• <strong>Generated content:</strong> Retained for service improvement (anonymized)</li>
          <li>• <strong>Usage data:</strong> Retained for analytics (aggregated and anonymized)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Access and download your data</li>
          <li>• Correct inaccurate information</li>
          <li>• Delete your account and data</li>
          <li>• Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>• Request data portability</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We use essential cookies for authentication and preferences. We do not use tracking cookies for advertising. 
          You can control cookie settings in your browser.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong>OpenAI:</strong> Processes your photos to generate captions (subject to OpenAI's privacy policy)</li>
          <li>• <strong>Stripe:</strong> Processes payments securely (subject to Stripe's privacy policy)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Uplo is not intended for use by anyone under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 18.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibent text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or want to exercise your rights, please contact us at 
          <a href="mailto:hello@getuplo.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@getuplo.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>